Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.55,0:32:34.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,If I were you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.55,0:32:36.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.55,0:32:38.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.55,0:32:41.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Tell me who you're playing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.55,0:32:43.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's something I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.55,0:32:47.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I was told
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.55,0:32:50.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,that I was in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.55,0:32:52.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,What should I do if I'm banned?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:54.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I just didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.55,0:32:55.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,One more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.55,0:32:56.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Let's start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.55,0:32:58.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Give me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.55,0:33:00.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,What should I do if I'm banned?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.55,0:33:01.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Are you going to abandon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.55,0:33:03.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I used to believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.55,0:33:05.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,it was for the sake of worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.55,0:33:07.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,God,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.55,0:33:09.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.55,0:33:11.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I was told
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.55,0:33:13.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,that I was in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.55,0:33:32.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,The sun is too bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.55,0:33:35.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's leaking from the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.55,0:33:38.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Until the darkness comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.55,0:33:42.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll keep running.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.55,0:33:44.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm banned,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.55,0:33:45.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,even if I'm noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.55,0:33:47.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,even if I'm told that I'm useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.55,0:33:50.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I can't be negative anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.55,0:33:51.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm banned,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.55,0:33:52.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,even if I'm noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.55,0:33:54.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,even if I'm told that I should stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.55,0:33:56.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.55,0:33:58.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,even if I'm told that I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.55,0:34:02.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,God, can't I do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.55,0:34:05.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Do you know where the standard is?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.55,0:34:09.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm driven into a situation like\Nthis,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.55,0:34:13.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will never be banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.55,0:34:35.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.55,0:35:04.55,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Rika Hachimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.23,0:35:35.23,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle that I was able to join a\Ngroup that I've liked for 7 years as a\N3rd generation student.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.23,0:35:43.23,ASS,,0,0,0,,Since I was little, I've been alone a\Nlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.23,0:35:47.23,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of what people would think\Nof me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.08,0:35:51.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was afraid to interact with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.08,0:35:59.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's one of the reasons I wanted to\Nchange myself and apply for the\Naudition.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.08,0:36:03.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.64,0:36:10.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,The performance I just showed you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.64,0:36:16.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,Among the three amazing students
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.64,0:36:24.64,ASS,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was very scared to be in\Nthe center
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.64,0:36:27.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.39,0:36:45.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,I did my best, and at the meet-and-\Ngreet, everyone complimented me, saying\Nthat I did well and that they were\Nlooking forward to it, so I was able to\Ndo my best today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.39,0:36:48.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.67,0:37:01.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,Everyone is so big to me, and I thought\NI needed everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.67,0:37:16.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best to contribute to\NSAKURADAKA46 from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.67,0:37:18.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.67,0:37:31.67,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.03,0:37:34.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Riko Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.03,0:37:38.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Before I joined Sakurazaka 46,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.03,0:37:45.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I often thought that I could still do it\Neven if I tried hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.03,0:37:49.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,But after I joined Sakurazaka 46,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.03,0:37:53.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I thought that I was doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.03,0:37:58.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,Now, as a member of Sakurazaka 46,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.03,0:37:59.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,and as a member of Sakurazaka 46,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.39,0:38:02.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,it's really fun to be able to do my\Nbest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.49,0:38:10.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to be an idol who can continue to\Nwork hard without forgetting to be\Ngrateful that there is a place to work\Nhard,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.89,0:38:20.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,and I want to be an idol who can make\NBUDDIES happy that I joined Sakurazaka\Nsomeday.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.89,0:38:23.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.39,0:38:31.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.11,0:38:40.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Reina Odakura, a 18-year-old high\Nschool student from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.11,0:38:44.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.11,0:38:48.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.11,0:38:56.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've been afraid of failing and getting\Nhurt since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.11,0:39:01.11,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've been looking at myself from the\Nmoment I took a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.11,0:39:03.09,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.33,0:39:05.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hated it so much that I couldn't help\Nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.49,0:39:12.17,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I gave up on Sakura Saka and tried\Nsomething completely different from what\NI've done so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.73,0:39:18.61,ASS,,0,0,0,,I tried a lot of new things, I failed a\Nlot, I cried a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.05,0:39:25.21,ASS,,0,0,0,,Every time I got over it with everyone\Nin the 3rd generation, I thought, "Am I\Ngrowing up?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.09,0:39:28.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.53,0:39:32.93,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't think life can be without scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.18,0:39:47.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,So, I want to be a person who can sit\Nnext to BUDDIES and have words and\Nexpressions that I can lean on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.18,0:39:52.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best from now on, so thank\Nyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.18,0:40:03.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,BUDDIES
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.80,0:40:08.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Nagisa Kojima, a 17-year-old high\Nschool student from Nagano prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.80,0:40:13.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've always loved idols since I was a\Nkid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.80,0:40:19.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,Last summer, I auditioned for an idol\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.80,0:40:25.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,Then I passed the audition for\N"Sakurazaka46".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.80,0:40:30.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:32.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,It was a training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.10,0:40:36.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was shooting a music video.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.10,0:40:46.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Of course, there were fun things, but\Nthere were a lot more painful,\Nfrustrating, and painful things than\Nthat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.10,0:40:57.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,But at that time, I met my ten friends\Nhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:41:01.10,ASS,,0,0,0,,Since then, I've experienced a lot of\Nthings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.86,0:41:09.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,A lot of bonds have been born, and my\Nfavorite words are "friendship" and\N"effort".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.86,0:41:18.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,The feeling of thinking about such\Nfriends is getting stronger and\Nstronger, and now I'm standing in front\Nof you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.86,0:41:30.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of thoughts about coming\Nthis far, but I'm really happy to be\Nable to stand in front of you with these\N11 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.07,0:41:50.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, I think there will be more\Ndifficult things, more fun things, and\Nmore fun things than the training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.07,0:42:01.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,At that time, I want to hold hands with\Nthese 11 people and BUDDIES and do my\Nbest to become an idol a year ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.23,0:42:05.23,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, so please continue to\Nsupport me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.23,0:42:07.23,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's all from Nagisa Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.85,0:42:23.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Hairi Taniguchi, 17 years old, from\NYamaguchi prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.85,0:42:30.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've been dreaming of becoming an idol\Nsince I was in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.85,0:42:40.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be on the first step of\Nmy dream of becoming an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.85,0:42:46.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,The place I've been dreaming of is so\Nbeautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.30,0:42:58.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,My family, who have been supporting me\Nfor a long time, came to see me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.30,0:43:01.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I have a younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.30,0:43:11.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,My younger brother told me that he would\Ngo to my first live today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.30,0:43:16.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,This is my first live performance in my\Nlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.69,0:43:21.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,My family told me that they wanted to go\Nto Sakurazaka 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.69,0:43:28.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,I really love that kind of family.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.69,0:43:39.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,And the BUDDIES who are watching me now\Nare watching me with very warm eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.69,0:43:44.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'm going to perform in\NSakurazaka 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.42,0:43:47.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.42,0:43:56.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I want to become a person who can\Nshine more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.42,0:43:59.42,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please continue to support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.03,0:44:16.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Izuki Nakashima, 20 years old, from\NFukuoka prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.03,0:44:24.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,My dream is to have you cheer for me\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.03,0:44:30.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I love the meet-and-greet I participated\Nin the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.03,0:44:34.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I love the live performance today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.03,0:44:40.03,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be able to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.03,0:44:43.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.39,0:44:56.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope that only good things will happen\Nto all the 3rd Gen students and all the\NBUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.39,0:45:02.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,But there may be times when that is not\Nthe case.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.39,0:45:10.39,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want them to remember me and feel\Nrelieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.02,0:45:14.02,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to be a strong presence for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.02,0:45:26.02,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will continue to cherish my bond with\Nthe 3rd generation and my time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.02,0:45:31.02,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best to lead a wonderful\Nlife as an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.02,0:45:33.02,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.02,0:45:43.02,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.79,0:45:48.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Mio Mato, 16 years old, from Fukuoka\Nprefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.79,0:45:53.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,I first met this group when I was in\Nelementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.79,0:46:05.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,I still vividly remember the shock I\Nfelt when I watched that performance on\NTV when I didn't know what being an idol\Nwas like.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.79,0:46:11.79,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've always been supportive of many\Ndifferent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.83,0:46:19.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,I want to be a person who can support\Nothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.83,0:46:21.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,If I didn't have that feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.83,0:46:26.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,and if I didn't happen to watch the TV\Nshow at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.83,0:46:32.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't think I would have been able to\Nstand in front of you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.83,0:46:41.83,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I want to be myself more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.97,0:47:08.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,The reason why I can be myself is\Nbecause of you who have been supporting\Nme for only 2 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.97,0:47:17.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,I can only feel this wonderful scenery\Ntoday, but I think it will be engraved\Nin my heart for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.97,0:47:24.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,My goal is to cheer someone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.04,0:47:28.04,ASS,,0,0,0,,That's why I joined this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.04,0:47:35.04,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best to become a beautiful\Nand strong idol like a cherry tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.04,0:47:43.04,ASS,,0,0,0,,And when I'm sad, I'd be happy if you\Ncould look at me and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.04,0:47:45.04,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.04,0:47:57.04,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.48,0:48:05.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Itoha Mukai, a 16-year-old high\Nschool student from Hiroshima\Nprefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.48,0:48:15.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm most happy in my life that I was\Nable to join my favorite Sakurazuka 46\Nas a 3rd year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.48,0:48:25.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,My life has changed 180 degrees since I\Nbecame a 3rd year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.48,0:48:28.48,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I have changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.34,0:48:32.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have changed a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.64,0:48:39.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,Negative, crybaby,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.34,0:48:45.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,and clumsy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.84,0:48:51.84,ASS,,0,0,0,,the ten people who warmly embraced me,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.84,0:48:57.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,and me, who still can't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.34,0:49:02.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,my seniors and managers who are kind to\Nme,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.74,0:49:11.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,and my BUDDIES who give me a lot of\Nhappiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.54,0:49:20.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was able to like myself a\Nlittle bit, which I hated so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.94,0:49:24.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm just supported by so many\Npeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.62,0:49:35.62,ASS,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to do anything, but\NI'm sure I'll bring you a lot of\Nhappiness one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.62,0:49:39.62,ASS,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.30,0:49:54.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuu Murai, 18 years old from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.30,0:50:01.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about what kind of\Nidol I want to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.30,0:50:04.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,so I'd like to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.30,0:50:10.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,BUDDIES have their own daily lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.30,0:50:14.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,and today was a happy day,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.30,0:50:16.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,and it was fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.30,0:50:18.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,but it was a little hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.30,0:50:20.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,and I had a lot of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.30,0:50:32.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think there are many days like that,\Nbut I hope I can always be by your side\Nand share my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.30,0:50:38.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,When you suddenly think about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.30,0:50:47.30,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope you feel better and feel lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.50,0:50:51.50,ASS,,0,0,0,,I think I'm very, very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.50,0:51:00.50,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm still inexperienced, but I hope I\Ncan continue to move forward with\Neveryone in the 3rd generation,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.50,0:51:05.50,ASS,,0,0,0,,and with my heart-warming, reliable, and\Ncool seniors,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.50,0:51:14.50,ASS,,0,0,0,,and with everyone in the warm and kind\NBUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.50,0:51:17.50,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.70,0:51:20.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.86,0:51:36.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Miyu Murayama, 18 years old from\NTokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.86,0:51:42.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to show my weakness to\Nothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.86,0:51:48.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,but I met 10 people who accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.86,0:51:55.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,And I met my favorite seniors in the\Nworld
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.86,0:52:01.86,ASS,,0,0,0,,through BUDDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.51,0:52:20.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was able to join the group that I love\Nthe most in the world and receive a lot\Nof happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.51,0:52:29.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,I hope I can join Sakurazaku 46 and make\Nsomeone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.51,0:52:35.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best, so please support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.51,0:52:44.51,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.19,0:52:52.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm Shizuki Yamashita, 18 years old,\Nfrom Kyoto Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.19,0:52:58.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to our 3rd\Ngeneration's opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.19,0:53:03.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was announced 2 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.19,0:53:12.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was worried if you would\Naccept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.19,0:53:16.19,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was worried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.24,0:53:22.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy that you welcomed me\Nwarmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.24,0:53:28.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've experienced a lot of emotions since\NI joined Asakurazuka46.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.24,0:53:32.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of fun and hard times,\Nbut...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.24,0:53:36.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,My most recent feeling is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.24,0:53:42.24,ASS,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to meet such a\Nwonderful 11 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.24,0:53:46.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you to everyone who has always\Nsupported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.18,0:54:00.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,I was very happy to meet you, and I\Nthink I wouldn't have been able to\Nexperience it if I hadn't joined\NSakurazaka 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.18,0:54:09.18,ASS,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for making my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.18,0:54:13.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will continue to create more and more\Nwonderful scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.94,0:54:18.94,ASS,,0,0,0,,I will do my best so that I can see it\Nwith everyone. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.74,0:54:44.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,Well then, this is the last song for\Ntoday's "Motenashi-kai".
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.74,0:54:45.74,ASS,,0,0,0,,Please listen to it.
