Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.00,0:55:05.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I thought ordinary days were normal
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.00,0:55:10.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,But they weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.00,0:55:15.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see you until today
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.00,0:55:20.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,There was a hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.00,0:55:29.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,The real loneliness isn't that there's\Nno one around
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.00,0:55:33.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,It's that I want to meet someone\Nimportant
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.00,0:55:38.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's love or not
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.00,0:55:43.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you can overcome it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.00,0:55:51.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.00,0:55:56.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,I've never forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.00,0:56:01.00,ASS,,0,0,0,,The days of cherry blossoms
